{"tid":848314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美副總統潘斯：中國用從美國偷來的技術 肆意化犁為劍","createTime":"2018-10-04T23:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T00:44:00.000Z","uid":35790,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72d0f1abe3b3c4c7f56207bfde66ee3e2cc110bf","tid":848314,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T23:43:54.000Z","msg":"潘斯：中國用從美國偷來的技術 肆意化犁為劍<br />\n<br />\n副總統潘斯在4日哈德遜研究所的演講中表示，美國企業在過去25年間幫助重振中國經濟，如今經濟實力強大起來的中國不但逼迫美企轉讓技術，上繳商業機密，更「運用從美國偷來的技術，肆意化犁為劍」。<br />\n潘斯說，中國政府如今口頭仍說「改革開放」，但「鄧小平這一著名的政策如今已成空話」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">他說，過去17年間，中國成為世界第二大經濟體，而這一成功很大程度上全因美國在中國的投資，「就像川普總統本周所說的，我們在過去25年間重建了中國。」</span><br />\n<br />\n潘斯說，如今中國通過「中國製造2025」計畫，著眼於控制世界上最先進產業的九成，包括機器人、生物科技、人工智能等；而為達成此目標，「北京指示其政府部門和企業動用一切手段去獲取美國智慧財產。」<br />\n<br />\n潘斯說，如今中國政府要求眾多美國企業若想在華發展業務，必須上交商業機密，同時也通過收購、並購美國企業，來獲取這些企業的新創產品。<br />\n<br />\n「最嚴重的是，中國的情報機關策畫大批竊取美國科技，包括最尖端的軍事藍圖」，潘斯說，「中共運用偷來的技術，正在大範圍內肆意化犁為劍。」<br />\n&lt;聯合&gt;"},{"pid":"cd61139c0b8e6c71eda053414d23968546b7cb2c","tid":848314,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T23:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da05990ebc3c94b6ac4a09d4e560646f6cfd66dd","tid":848314,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T23:45:36.000Z","msg":"支那成日吹&quot;亮劍&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb52f700c5165b042f6519fd41f588899af3dc96","tid":848314,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da05990ebc3c94b6ac4a09d4e560646f6cfd66dd","tid":848314,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T23:45:36.000Z","msg":"支那成日吹&quot;亮劍&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T23:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4d9f67072bc8499296d92ec113ca2ef539127a","tid":848314,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T00:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a431200af68eebc7064fdd4786a82398237b7ac","tid":848314,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T00:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62997a54a9e70c85ad39ada343a9fca8c9d191a","tid":848314,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T00:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總統副總統帶領FBI CIA 國防部 外交部 財政部 參眾兩院 朝野兩黨 海陸空三軍打到黎<br />\n中共上下資產被凍結冇得避<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace51b25163f18ce0e08c601f163fc3050da70f4","tid":848314,"uid":18955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T00:44:00.000Z","msg":"一鋪就令你回到解放前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}